  <POU Name="CycleTimeRecorderCommands" Id="{80d6ef78-3ed7-45b5-b0ed-cfde5944d415}" SpecialFunc="None">
    <Declaration><![CDATA[(* 
## Short summary

This class is a collection of cycle time recorder commands that provides a fluent interface for single attempt commands, which can be evaluated by a cycle manager instance.
### Example 
```
	cycleManager.leave(
		cycleTimeRecorder.commands.captureCurrentCycle(
			additionalMessage := 'just an example'
		)
	);  
	```

